OL,3,CPlanning inspector backs council in
OL,4,Clisted building banners row
OL,6,FThe government's planning inspector
OL,7,Fhas backed Bradford Council in a
OL,8,Fdispute with the owners of a listed
OL,9,Fformer library covered in advertising
OL,10,Fbanners.
OL,12,FThe council issued an enforcement
OL,13,Fnotice against Uneekhomes Real Estate,
OL,14,Fthe owners of the Grade II-listed
OL,15,Fformer Great Horton Library, on Cross
OL,16,FLane, in March 2024.
OL,18,FIt required them to remove 14
OL,19,Funauthorised banners within a month.
