OL,6,F"However, I am not persuaded that the
OL,7,Fbanners installed were the minimum
OL,8,Fnecessary to achieve the aims of
OL,9,Fhealth, safety or preservation of the
OL,10,Fbuilding.
OL,12,F"Whilst the banners are vibrant, they
OL,13,Falso appear incongruous on this
OL,14,Fhistoric building by reason of their
OL,15,Fscale, use of materials, and
OL,16,Fadvertisement content.
