OL,6,F"Moreover, the banners obscure large
OL,7,Fparts of the historic fabric of the
OL,8,Fbuilding, including stone mullions and
OL,9,Ftransoms, and not just the window
OL,10,Fframes and glazing."
OL,12,FShe said clear film or Perspex over
OL,13,Fthe windows would have provided
OL,14,Fsufficient protection.
